snippet.title: Negative Space, a free puzzle game for Android
snippet.description:
Negative Space is a free puzzle game for Android Smartphones.

Draw in black or white on the screen, to create paths and push the little blobs to their respective flag.

Android market link : https://market.android.com/details?id=net.sbr.negativespace
